com.facebook.litho.annotations

Annotation Type PropSetter


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
public @interface PropSetter
    Indicates that a method implementation sets Prop. It is intended to be used on the generated Component.Builder method.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      boolean required 
      java.lang.String value
